  m_text: "Drawing: Players can draw a card into their hand, costing 3 Mna. \r\n\r\nPlaying:
    For a card to perform actions, it needs to be played from a player\u2019s hand
    to their island, costing an amount of Mna equal to the amount of squares in the
    card\u2019s Grid Shape. "
