      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Cardestia is a 1v1 card game. The objective of the game is to destroy
    your opponent\u2019s island by reducing their Life Points (LP) to 0. To achieve
    this, players use their cards to take actions using Manna (Mna). \r\n\r\nEach
    player has their own pool of Mna that they use to perform all of their actions.
    Each turn the player gains Mna equal to the number of empty spaces on their board
    at the start of each round. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
